<h1>Topic Folder: <%= @topic.name %></h1>

If you'd like to change this Topic's Name, click <a href=<%="/topics/#{@topic.slug}/edit"%>>here</a>.
<br><br>


Click the button below if you want to delete this entire Topic Folder and its links. <br>
(CAREFUL, you can't undo this action!) <br>
<form action="/topics/<%= @topic.slug %>/delete" method="post">
  <input type="hidden" id="hidden" name="_method" value="delete">
  <input type="submit" value="Delete Topic">

</form>
